Conveniently nestled on the edge of town in a quiet residential neighborhood and still close to schools, parks, & shopping.  

The MAIN FLOOR features an open style concept.  The kitchen, dining room, and living room give to an open floor plan.  White kitchen cabinets and recent decorating updates give a farmhouse feel.  This kitchen also features a large island peninsula that allows for plenty of counter workspace.  Did I mention cabinets galore!  More than enough cabinets to supply all your kitchen storage needs.  Two main floor bedrooms, one being a master bedroom featuring a luxurious en suite master bath with Jacuzzi tub and large walk-in closet. Captivating double french doors give way to a newly renovated bedroom (non-conforming) also featuring recess lighting.  A work room, laundry room, and quarter bath are also located on this level.  OH THE POSSIBILTIES!  The fourth bedroom (non-conforming) you will find as a bit of a blank slate. Perennial landscaping with fountain and night lighting add that little extra touch to the outdoor features.  A single detached garage with garage door opener and separate storage shed complete this property.

Newer energy efficient exterior doors and quality full view back & front screen doors.  Refrigerator, dishwasher, stove, sump pump (w/ back up battery), water softener, washer & dryer are included in the sale of this home.
